data.description: Welcome home to this delightful 3BR/2BA single-story home in Mount Olive! This home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, starting with a cozy covered porch perfect for relaxing evenings. Step inside to discover a bright and airy living space bathed in natural light, enhancing the home's welcoming feel. The heart of this home is the open kitchen, boasting ample cabinet and counter space, complemented by an updated backsplash and a convenient eat-in area. Each of the sizable bedrooms promises comfort and tranquility, while the two full bathrooms, featuring single vanities and tub/shower combos, cater to both convenience and functionality. Step outside to the huge fenced backyard, an ideal space for outdoor activities and gardening, complete with a shed/workshop for all your creative projects or extra storage needs. This home is a great blend of comfort, style, and practicality, waiting for you to make it your own! Schedule your viewing today!
